oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Apollo 12 - Moon travel tapes - Tape 3 Side 1 PT. 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tape 3 (Side 1) [Part 2] of an unknown number of tapes. Program sent on the Apollo 12 space mission for astronaut's enjoyment. Originally from a cassette Tape. Featuring Charley Pride, David Houston, and Dan Gibson.
